nodes.text: The Ku'Bakai system or Kubindi system was a star system located within the Calaron sector in the Outer Rim Territories region of the galaxy. It contained Kubindi, homeworld of the Kubaz species, Ku'Bakai 6, Ku'Bakai 8, Ku'Bakai 11, and the primary star Ku'Bakai. The Kubaz colonized several habitable planets within the Ku'Bakai system.
